page.title: 16A 12 year olds day.
page.content: I get up at 08.00 and have a{wash,}go downstairs,get dressed and have my {breakfast}which is usually {Cornflakes.}At 09.00 I switch on the television and wait for my friend and his parents to come and take me{B.M.X. {racing.}We go in their big van with our bikes.We go to different places each week,such as{Newark}and {Nottingham. First I practice around the track,then we begin.I am usually {number 27.}I race three times then we have a final and I often come fifth or sixth. We set off for home about 20.00.When I get home I have a bath then a pile of sandwiches in front of the television.I am usually in bed by 21.30.
